1. Fork this project (using darcs; clone / fork from hub.darcs.net:jcast/globalscript).
2. Push changes to your fork.
3. Email me at jonathanccast@fastmail.fm.
4. I'll mention your fork on the globalscript.org website.
5. If I like your changes, I'll pull from your fork. I might also have suggestions for you if I feel like it!
6. If you bug me about responding to you, I'll set up an email filter to throw away your emails.
